---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Primorum — AI-native venture builder">
  <p class="eyebrow">Primorum &mdash; Toronto, 2026</p>

  <h1 class="hero">
    A venture builder where AI is the operator and one human signs the cheques.
  </h1>

  <p class="lede">
    The next generation of software companies will not be built by larger and larger engineering
    teams. They will be built by capital allocators with a fleet of AI agents shipping the product,
    doing the support, running the marketing, and closing the books. We are starting that company.
  </p>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <p class="eyebrow">The bet</p>
  <h2 style="margin-top:0;">Three things at once, all contested.</h2>

  <ul class="bets">
    <li>
      <div class="label">01 &mdash; Capability</div>
      <p class="claim">
        Foundation models crossed the operator threshold in 2026. End-to-end workflows are now
        solved, not demoable.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="label">02 &mdash; Cost</div>
      <p class="claim">
        Per-task inference costs have collapsed by roughly 10&times; in 24 months. AI ops is cheaper
        than the cheapest human in any country.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="label">03 &mdash; Distribution</div>
      <p class="claim">
        Models and tooling are commoditizing. Getting the product in front of the right person at
        the right moment is not. Distribution is the binding constraint.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <p class="eyebrow">Operating rules</p>
  <h2 style="margin-top:0;">Four constraints every experiment must respect.</h2>

  <ul class="rules">
    <li>
      <div class="num">Rule 01</div>
      <div class="rule">AI-native distribution.</div>
      <p>Platform-native, programmatic, or audience-piggyback. No human-led sales.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="num">Rule 02</div>
      <div class="rule">AI is the operator.</div>
      <p>The product <em>is</em> the business. If a human is required in the loop, re-scope or kill.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="num">Rule 03</div>
      <div class="rule">Greenfield only.</div>
      <p>No reviving old projects, no pivoting dead spikes. Start clean every time.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="num">Rule 04</div>
      <div class="rule">Path to $1M.</div>
      <p>Written-down unit economics &times; distribution &times; market size. No vibes.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <p>
    Read the full <a href="/thesis">thesis</a>, or reach the principal at
    <a href="mailto:brendan@primorum.ai">brendan@primorum.ai</a>.
  </p>
</Base>
